But to be honest,
the printing cost is tremendous.

6
00:00:17,750 --> 00:00:20,310
You're always wearing
really cute clothes.

7
00:00:20,380 --> 00:00:22,940
Justice makes them for me.

8
00:00:35,860 --> 00:00:37,530
Chance to get up!

