Friendship that'll last a lifetime!

24
00:01:23,850 --> 00:01:28,980
It's not like a hero,
but you feel something.

25
00:01:29,050 --> 00:01:32,750
You, me, who? This, that?
Him, anyone's okay!

26
00:01:32,820 --> 00:01:34,150
Anywhere it is!

27
